sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Client as CLI/TUI/Web/Desktop
  participant Server as Server or In-Process Adapter
  participant Session as Session Processor
  participant Provider as Provider/LLM Stream
  participant Tools as Tool Registry and Permissions
  participant Store as Storage and Event Stream

  User->>Client: Enter prompt or command
  Client->>Server: Create, fork, continue, or prompt session
  Server->>Session: Dispatch request in workspace/instance context
  Session->>Provider: Build messages and stream model response
  Provider-->>Session: Text, tool calls, usage, finish events
  Session->>Tools: Resolve available tools and permission checks
  Tools-->>Session: Tool results or approval requirements
  Session->>Store: Persist message parts, events, cost, and state
  Store-->>Client: Stream updates for rendering
  Client-->>User: Show text, tool activity, errors, and completion
